title: Stade de Mbour
text:
Stade de Mbour is a <a href="Senegal">Senegal</a>ese <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Mbour">Mbour</a>. They currently play in the Senegal Premier League.
They played the 2010 season in the top division in Senegalese football and were part of the Senegal Ligue 2. Their home stadium is <a href="Stade%20Municipal%20de%20Mbour">Stade Municipal de Mbour</a>.
